      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "|"                  to   w-lin-imm-brv-001
                                               w-lin-imm-brv-002
                                               w-lin-imm-brv-003
                                               w-lin-imm-brv-004      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Visualizzazione griglia                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      80                   to   v-car                  .
           move      08                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
