      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-stp-prn-flg-int    not  = spaces
                     go to prn-rou-pri-831.
           perform   prn-fin-lr3-000      thru prn-fin-lr3-999        .
       prn-rou-pri-831.
           exit.
       prn-rou-pri-840.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Esecuzione per fine 4. livello di rottura       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
