      *              * Numero linee di stampa minimo                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      01                   to   w-stp-stp-lin-min      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Bottom margin in linee                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      0                    to   w-stp-stp-bot-lin      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Ampiezza caratteri                              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-stp-stp-amp-car      .
